<a0:script hash="0" id_diff_z1z="75" isExtraChild="1" level="3" match="0" type="text/javascript" value_z1z="">
window.is_mobile = Boolean(navigator.userAgent.match(/(iphone)|(ipod)|(ipad)|(android)|(blackberry)|(windows phone)|(symbian)/i));
var switchTo5x=true;
var googletag = googletag || {};
googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];
function get_base_url() {
	port = '';
	if (document.location.port) {
		port = ':'+ document.location.port
	}
	return document.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.hostname + port ;
}

function stickyAd() {
	var prime = $('#panel-prime'),
		panelPrimeBottom = prime.offset().top + prime.height(),
		footer_top = $('#footer').position().top,
		main_top = $('#main_container').position().top,
		ad_height = $("#skyscraper").height(),
		scrollTop = $(this).scrollTop(),
		left_side_longer = Boolean($("#page_content_left").height() &gt; $("#page_content_right").height());

	//fix pos if scrolled past panel-prime
	if (scrollTop &gt; panelPrimeBottom &amp;&amp; left_side_longer) {
		if (scrollTop + ad_height + 20 &gt; footer_top) {
			$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'absolute');
			$('#skyscraper').css('top', footer_top - ad_height -20 - main_top +'px');
		} else {
			$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'fixed');
			$('#skyscraper').css('top','10px');
		}
	} else {
		$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'static');
	}
}


$(document).ready(function () {
	$(window).scroll(function (event) {
		stickyAd();
	});

	map = ["/time-zone", "/info", "/time-gadgets", "/timepiece"]
	map.forEach(function(item, idx) {
		var tab = idx +1;
		if (window.location.pathname.indexOf(item)==0) {
			$("#gtab" + tab).addClass("active");
			$("#mtab" + tab).addClass("active");
		}
		else {
			$("#gtab" + tab).removeClass("active");
			$("#mtab" + tab).removeClass("active");
		}
	} )
});

(function() {
	var gads = document.createElement('script');
	gads.async = true;
	gads.type = 'text/javascript';
	var useSSL = 'https:' == document.location.protocol;
	var scheme = (useSSL ? 'https:' : 'http:');
	gads.src = scheme + '//www.googletagservices.com/tag/js/gpt.js';
	var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
	node.parentNode.insertBefore(gads, node);
})();
var gptAdSlots = [];
googletag.cmd.push(function() {
    googletag.pubads().setTargeting('env',"live"); // define if editor or live
    googletag.pubads().setTargeting('pagetype', pageType )
    // define skyscraper sizes
    // Show at 300x600, only on 1200*200 or larger
    var mappingSky = googletag.sizeMapping().
        addSize([0, 0], []).
        addSize([1200, 200], [300, 600]). // Desktop only
        build();
    // define banner sizes
    // Show at 300x100 on small screens
    // 468x60 when &gt;= 768 (tablet)
    // 728x90 when &gt;= 1200 (desktop)
    var mappingBanners = googletag.sizeMapping().
        addSize([0, 0], [300, 100]).
        addSize([768, 200], [468, 60]).
        addSize([1200, 200], [728, 90]).
        build();

	var mappingInContent = googletag.sizeMapping().
	   addSize([0, 0], [300, 250]).
	   addSize([728, 200], [728, 90]).
	   build();

	var mappingRHSMPU = googletag.sizeMapping().
	   addSize([0, 0], []).
	   addSize([992, 250], [300, 250]).
	   build();

    gptAdSlots[1] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_BANNER_ATF', [300, 100], 'masthead').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingBanners).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

    gptAdSlots[2] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_RH_SKY', [300, 600], 'skyscraper').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingSky).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

    gptAdSlots[3] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_EOC', [300, 100], 'endofcontent').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingBanners).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

	gptAdSlots[4] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_Mid_Content', [[300, 250], [728, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1465990184833-0')
	.defineSizeMapping(mappingInContent)
	.addService(googletag.pubads());

	 .defineSizeMapping(mappingRHSMPU)
	.addService(googletag.pubads());

    googletag.enableServices();
});

    $( "#search-btn" ).click(function() {
        $('#search-btn').toggleClass('active');
        $('#more-btn').removeClass('active');
        $('#mobile-search-box').toggle('fast');
        $('#more-menu').hide('fast');
    });

    $( "#more-btn" ).click(function() {
        $('#more-btn').toggleClass('active');
        $('#search-btn').removeClass('active');
        $('#more-menu').toggle('fast');
        $('#mobile-search-box').hide('fast');

<a0:h2 hash="0" id_diff_z1z="286" level="9" match="0" value_z1z="">Time in GMT right now</a0:h2>
<a0:p hash="0" id_diff_z1z="287" level="9" match="0" value_z1z="a0:b a0:b a0:a ">The United Kingdom runs on <a0:b hash="0" id_diff_z1z="288" level="10" match="0" value_z1z="">GMT</a0:b> only during Winter months and on <a0:b hash="0" id_diff_z1z="289" level="10" match="0" value_z1z="">BST</a0:b> during Summer months: <a0:a hash="0" href="/info/bst/" id_diff_z1z="290" level="10" match="0" value_z1z=""> British Summer Time </a0:a> </a0:p>
<a0:div hash="0" id_diff_z1z="291" level="9" match="0" ng-app="svgClock" value_z1z="a0:div ">
<a0:div class="row" hash="0" id_diff_z1z="292" level="10" match="0" value_z1z="a0:clock-panel a0:clock-panel ">

<a0:script hash="0" id_diff_z1z="75" isExtraChild="1" level="3" match="0" type="text/javascript" value_z1z="">
window.is_mobile = Boolean(navigator.userAgent.match(/(iphone)|(ipod)|(ipad)|(android)|(blackberry)|(windows phone)|(symbian)/i));
var switchTo5x=true;
var googletag = googletag || {};
googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];
function get_base_url() {
	port = '';
	if (document.location.port) {
		port = ':'+ document.location.port
	}
	return document.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.hostname + port ;
}

function stickyAd() {
	var prime = $('#panel-prime'),
		panelPrimeBottom = prime.offset().top + prime.height(),
		footer_top = $('#footer').position().top,
		main_top = $('#main_container').position().top,
		ad_height = $("#skyscraper").height(),
		scrollTop = $(this).scrollTop(),
		left_side_longer = Boolean($("#page_content_left").height() &gt; $("#page_content_right").height());

	//fix pos if scrolled past panel-prime
	if (scrollTop &gt; panelPrimeBottom &amp;&amp; left_side_longer) {
		if (scrollTop + ad_height + 20 &gt; footer_top) {
			$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'absolute');
			$('#skyscraper').css('top', footer_top - ad_height -20 - main_top +'px');
		} else {
			$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'fixed');
			$('#skyscraper').css('top','10px');
		}
	} else {
		$('#skyscraper').css('position', 'static');
	}
}


$(document).ready(function () {
	$(window).scroll(function (event) {
		stickyAd();
	});

	map = ["/time-zone", "/info", "/time-gadgets", "/timepiece"]
	map.forEach(function(item, idx) {
		var tab = idx +1;
		if (window.location.pathname.indexOf(item)==0) {
			$("#gtab" + tab).addClass("active");
			$("#mtab" + tab).addClass("active");
		}
		else {
			$("#gtab" + tab).removeClass("active");
			$("#mtab" + tab).removeClass("active");
		}
	} )
});

(function() {
	var gads = document.createElement('script');
	gads.async = true;
	gads.type = 'text/javascript';
	var useSSL = 'https:' == document.location.protocol;
	var scheme = (useSSL ? 'https:' : 'http:');
	gads.src = scheme + '//www.googletagservices.com/tag/js/gpt.js';
	var node = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
	node.parentNode.insertBefore(gads, node);
})();
var gptAdSlots = [];
googletag.cmd.push(function() {
    googletag.pubads().setTargeting('env',"live"); // define if editor or live
    googletag.pubads().setTargeting('pagetype', pageType )
    // define skyscraper sizes
    // Show at 300x600, only on 1200*200 or larger
    var mappingSky = googletag.sizeMapping().
        addSize([0, 0], []).
        addSize([1200, 200], [300, 600]). // Desktop only
        build();
    // define banner sizes
    // Show at 300x100 on small screens
    // 468x60 when &gt;= 768 (tablet)
    // 728x90 when &gt;= 1200 (desktop)
    var mappingBanners = googletag.sizeMapping().
        addSize([0, 0], [300, 100]).
        addSize([768, 200], [468, 60]).
        addSize([1200, 200], [728, 90]).
        build();

	var mappingInContent = googletag.sizeMapping().
	   addSize([0, 0], [300, 250]).
	   addSize([728, 200], [728, 90]).
	   build();

	var mappingRHSMPU = googletag.sizeMapping().
	   addSize([0, 0], []).
	   addSize([992, 250], [300, 250]).
	   build();

    gptAdSlots[1] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_BANNER_ATF', [300, 100], 'masthead').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingBanners).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

    gptAdSlots[2] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_RH_SKY', [300, 600], 'skyscraper').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingSky).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

    gptAdSlots[3] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_EOC', [300, 100], 'endofcontent').
    defineSizeMapping(mappingBanners).
    setCollapseEmptyDiv(true).
    addService(googletag.pubads());

	gptAdSlots[4] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_Mid_Content', [[300, 250], [728, 90]], 'div-gpt-ad-1465990184833-0')
	.defineSizeMapping(mappingInContent)
	.addService(googletag.pubads());

	gptAdSlots[5] = googletag.defineSlot('/32639920/GMT_RHS_MPU', [300, 250], 'GMT_RHS_MPU')
	 .defineSizeMapping(mappingRHSMPU)
	.addService(googletag.pubads());

    googletag.enableServices();
});

    // Open close search based on selection of search item

    $( "#search-btn" ).click(function() {
        $('#search-btn').toggleClass('active');
        $('#more-btn').removeClass('active');
        $('#mobile-search-box').toggle('fast');
        $('#more-menu').hide('fast');
    });

    $( "#more-btn" ).click(function() {
        $('#more-btn').toggleClass('active');
        $('#search-btn').removeClass('active');
        $('#more-menu').toggle('fast');
        $('#mobile-search-box').hide('fast');
    });
